  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support to Vulnerable Malian Refugees and Selected Host and IDP Communities Through Livelihoods and Protection Activities in the North and Sahel Regions of Burkina Faso- PHASE III</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This third phase project seeks to reinforce social cohesion and strengthen resilience of populations affected by the crisis in Burkina Faso. In particular, this project will assist affected populations through an increase in both joint and targeted livelihoods opportunities and access to protection for vulnerable asylum seekers and selected internally displaced persons and host communities in the North region of Burkina Faso.</narrative>
  </description>
